    <title>常用放大器</title>
    <url>/2020/03/23/%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E6%94%BE%E5%A4%A7%E5%99%A8/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="反向比例放大器"><a href="#反向比例放大器" class="headerlink" title="反向比例放大器"></a>反向比例放大器</h1><p><img src="https://pic.downk.cc/item/5e782fc45c560911295744a1.jpg" alt="1"></p>
<p>$$<br>V_{out}=-\frac{R_f}{R}V_{in}<br>$$</p>
<h1 id="反向加法器"><a href="#反向加法器" class="headerlink" title="反向加法器"></a>反向加法器</h1><p><img src="https://pic.downk.cc/item/5e78300b5c560911295782a0.jpg" alt="2"><br>$$<br>V_{out}=-\frac{R_f}{R}(V_{in1}+V_{in2})<br>$$</p>
<h1 id="减法器"><a href="#减法器" class="headerlink" title="减法器"></a>减法器</h1><p><img src="https://pic.downk.cc/item/5e78302d5c56091129579e0e.jpg" alt="3"><br>$$<br>V_{out}=\frac{R_f}{R}(V_{in2}-V_{in1})<br>$$</p>
<h1 id="同向比例放大器"><a href="#同向比例放大器" class="headerlink" title="同向比例放大器"></a>同向比例放大器</h1><p><img src="https://pic.downk.cc/item/5e7831085c56091129589f30.jpg" alt="4"><br>$$<br>V_{out}=\frac{R_2}{R_1}V_{in}<br>$$</p>
<h1 id="微分器"><a href="#微分器" class="headerlink" title="微分器"></a>微分器</h1><p><img src="https://pic.downk.cc/item/5e78311c5c5609112958b398.jpg" alt="5"><br>$$<br>V_{out}=-RC\frac{d}{dt}V_{in}<br>$$</p>
<h1 id="积分器"><a href="#积分器" class="headerlink" title="积分器"></a>积分器</h1><p><img src="https://pic.downk.cc/item/5e7831325c5609112958c724.jpg" alt="6"><br>$$<br>V_{out}=-\frac{1}{RC}\int V_{in}dt<br>$$</p>
]]></content>
